        "management": "First-line: echinocandin (caspofungin 70mg load, 50mg daily; micafungin 100mg daily; anidulafungin 200mg load, 100mg daily). Step-down to fluconazole if C. albicans/parapsilosis and stable. Remove central line. Fundoscopic exam. Duration: 14 days after clearance."
