        "management": "Induction: liposomal AmB 3-4mg/kg/day + flucytosine 100mg/kg/day x2 weeks (or minimum 1 week). Consolidation: fluconazole 400-800mg/day x8 weeks. Maintenance: fluconazole 200mg/day. Therapeutic lumbar puncture for elevated ICP."
