        "management": "First-line: liposomal AmB 5-10mg/kg/day. Surgical debridement (mandatory, often multiple). Control underlying risk factors (correct ketoacidosis, reduce immunosuppression). Step-down to posaconazole or isavuconazole after improvement. Duration: until resolution."
