        "management": "Prophylaxis: posaconazole (preferred), voriconazole, or micafungin in high-risk patients. Empiric: caspofungin or liposomal AmB for neutropenic fever >96h on broad antibiotics. Preemptive: start when biomarkers positive + clinical/imaging findings."
